body:
This PR adds one new package needed for a forthcoming CMSSW PR
- [AXOL1TL](https://github.com/cms-hls4ml/AXOL1TL): level-1 global trigger anomaly detection emulator

This follows a similar PR recently made: https://github.com/cms-sw/cmsdist/pull/8307
